            <bug_when>2009-02-08 05:17:55 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>The Table widget now has a cleaner interface to the column visibility menu, including interface definitions (IColumnMenuButton and IColumnMenuItem) for authors wishing to create their own column visibility menus. One example of such an alternative menu was provided by Bill Adams. His implementation has been modified to meet the interface definition, and is now available in qooxdoo.contrib as the TableColumnMenuGrid project. A demo resides in that project showing its use.

Derrell
</thetext>
